              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "-To reconstruct the angle between the neutron and",
                " outgoing charged particle, in the telescope two",
                " position-sensitive multistep chambers were installed.",
                "-Deuterons together with other low-energy charged part.",
                " were separated from the elastically scattered protons",
                " online and data were recorded event-by-event."
              ]
            }
          ],
          "DETECTOR": [
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "TELES",
                "SCIN",
                "SCIN"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                "",
                "Two scintillation counters, which served for energy",
                "determination (ede method) and particle separation(TOF)"
              ]
            },
            {
              "pointer": "",
              "coded_information": [
                "MWPC"
              ],
              "free_text": [
                " 2 multiwire proportional counters.",
                "The first operated as veto detector and the second one",
                "provided a coincidence signal which ensured that all",
                "detected particles were produced within the gas cell.",
                "The hydrogen gas target is used as counter gas.",
                "* Two position-sensitive multistep chambers were used",
                "for determination of the track coordinates in order to",
                "reconstruct the neutron-deuteron angle."
              ]
            }
